HEADWORD: Encourager
<hw>En*cour"a*ger</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who
encourages, incites, or helps forward; a favorer.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The pope is . . . a great <qex>encourager</qex> of arts.</q>
<rj><qau>Addison.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Encouraging</ent>⟦br⟧
